### Key Terms and Definitions

| Term             | Definition                                             | Example / Notes                           |
|------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Widget           | basic blocking of a flutter app everything is a widget.|Text, Image, container,column              |
| MaterialApp      | the root of the app. Sets up the themes                |found main dart                            |
| Scaffold         | provides basic visual layouts                          |each screen uses it                        |
| StatelessWidget  | predefined paths to navigate between screens           | used on my home page                      |
| StatefulWidget   | a widget that can change over time                     | most of the screeb files                  |
| Navigator        |                                                        |navigator,puhNamed(context, '/page2');     |
| AppBar           | Top navigation bar                                     |title of each page appears                 |
| Column           | vertical layout                                        |                                           |
| Row              | horizontal layout                                      |                                           |
| Container        | wraps content with padding margin or color             |                                           |
| Text             | displays text                                          |                                           |
| Image.network    | displays images from a URL                             |                                           |

